Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools: Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Set Up Einstein Discovery: Get Started Using Einstein Discovery, Build Models in Einstein Discovery, Define Your Target Outcome, Prepare Data for Analysis, Create and Manage Models.

Explore Data Insights: Navigate Data Insights, Data Insights Interface, Interact with Data Insights, Explore Insights for a Variable, Compare Subgroups with the Global Average.

Predict & Improve Outcomes: Predictions and Improvements, Bookmark an Insight in a Model, Get Descriptive and Diagnostic Insights Programmatically, Manage and Deploy Models in Einstein Discovery.
title: Navigating Data Insights in Salesforce
